column2: "Hiya. Have you talked to Zect and the others yet? If you haven't, go see them already."
"The menus you get in cafes are so cute!"
"One roasted soybeans, octopus and wasabi, stingray fins, stewed beef tendons and chicken meatballs coming right up!"
"On Sundays, I like to take my time Gathering."
"It's a really great way to relax."
"Nice work. Zect said he had loads of fun! I'm glad you all had a good time."
"Makes me want to start giving you orders again. I hope I get another chance soon~."
"He wants to enjoy being a Cast in a new way? And he wants to know what accessories would be good for that...? Really?"
"Always the difficult questions from Zect. Hmm... Now what might work?"
"Oh, I know. How about a \"Bunny Ears Ribbon\", or maybe a \"Waist Tied Jersey\"?"
"I dunno if they'd work on a mecha. But you never know, right?"
